snippet.title: Paranormal Tales Game  - Official Announcement Teaser Trailer
snippet.description:
Wishlist, if you dare: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2193600/Paranormal_Tales

My friend and I are making a bodycam style horror game inspired by P.T. where you're lost in a hyper realistic forest and must find your dog, Teddy.

Thanks so much for your support!

• Website: https://dontplaypt.com/
• Discord: https://discord.gg/7G3KFyjpFK
• Twitter:  https://twitter.com/DontPlayPT
• Patreon: https://www.patreon.com/ParanormalTales

#gaming #paranormaltales
